OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,FITV News' Sabet Choudhury sat down
OL,7,Fwith Syd Lawrence to talk about his
OL,8,Fdiagnosis
OL,10,FCricket legend David 'Syd' Lawrence
OL,11,Fhas spoken out on coming to terms with
OL,12,Fthe "complete shock" of being
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with motor neurone disease.
OL,15,FThe former Gloucestershire and England
OL,16,Ffast bowler was diagnosed with the
OL,17,Fcondition in June following what he
OL,18,Fthought would be a straightforward
OL,19,Foperation on his knee.
