OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,FHe sat down with ITV News West Country
OL,7,Fpresenter Sabet Choudhury to talk
OL,8,Fabout the last six months and
OL,9,Faccepting that he cannot beat MND.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think Rob Burrows said
OL,12,F'with this disease, you've got to be
OL,13,Fbrave' - and you have got to be brave
OL,14,Fbecause it's bloody scary. It really
OL,15,Fis.
OL,17,F"You know this is the way you're going
OL,18,Fto die and it will get you at some
OL,19,Fstage.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
