OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"No matter how much of a warrior I am,
OL,7,FI know that I can't win this fight. It
OL,8,Fwill defeat me. All I can do is give a
OL,9,Fvery good fight but I can't win, I
OL,10,Fknow that, so you have to come to
OL,11,Fterms with that."
OL,13,FCasting his mind back to the
OL,14,Fdiagnosis, Syd described how it was
OL,15,Fcompletely unexpected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
