OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"I went in for a knee operation of
OL,7,Fthat famous left knee and so we had
OL,8,Fknee replacements and after three
OL,9,Fmonths I noticed I wasn't recovering.
OL,10,FAnd after four months, the other leg
OL,11,Fwent.
OL,13,F"After all this time I was still on
OL,14,Fcrutches and then it kind of spread to
OL,15,Fthe rest of my body.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
