OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"By April I couldn't walk at all. So
OL,7,Fwithin the space of six months, I
OL,8,Fwasn't able to walk and then I ended
OL,9,Fup inside the hospital for three
OL,10,Fmonths for them to try and give me a
OL,11,Fdiagnosis.
OL,13,F"Then by June, they told me the news
OL,14,Fwhich I wasn't expecting. It was a
OL,15,Fcomplete shock," he said.
OL,17,FHe added that he felt "numb, like he
OL,18,Fwas in a bad dream" and immediately
OL,19,Fthought about Rob Burrows.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
