OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"I suppose what scares me is that the
OL,7,Fquality of life I will have at the
OL,8,Fend. That's what I'm not looking
OL,9,Fforward to.
OL,11,F"This disease is cruel and it's
OL,12,Ftowards the end when you haven't got
OL,13,Fthe capacity to speak, to communicate
OL,14,Fand that side of it is not nice."
OL,16,FSyd has taken steps to ensure he feels
OL,17,Fas much like himself as possible,
OL,18,Fright until the end, by creating a
OL,19,Fvoice bank that will allow a computer
OL,20,Fto speak for him - in his voice - when
OL,21,Fhe loses his speech.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
