OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,FBut he added that he is trying not to
OL,7,Fthink about the future too much -
OL,8,F"that'll just scramble your brain", he
OL,9,Fexplained.
OL,11,F"You've got to be in the present and
OL,12,Flive in the moment and process it. It
OL,13,Ftook me a long time to process it.
OL,15,F"I wouldn't say that I ever felt
OL,16,Fdepressed because I don't think that
OL,17,Fis me, but you do feel like you have a
OL,18,Fbad day but you soon get over it with
OL,19,Fthe support of your family and your
OL,20,Ffriends.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
