OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"And once you process it, you've just
OL,7,Fgot to get on with life as best you
OL,8,Fcan and with the support of so many
OL,9,Ffriends, it's been overwhelming."
OL,11,FSyd's diagnosis has also been a lot
OL,12,Ffor his family and friends to take in,
OL,13,Fand learn to live with.
OL,15,FHe said: "They've taken it tough. My
OL,16,Fwife, she's taken it really tough but
OL,17,Fwe have to support each other and
OL,18,Fthat's all you can do. And my son's
OL,19,Fbeen brilliant. He's been
OL,20,Funbelievable."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
