OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,FSyd added that he had "always been a
OL,7,Fperson with a positive mindset" and he
OL,8,Fwas trying to carry that approach into
OL,9,Fthis new phase of life.
OL,11,F"Don't beat yourself up about it. Just
OL,12,Fknow that don't let it dictate your
OL,13,Fday if you have a bad morning, that
OL,14,Fmeans you're going to have a bad day.
OL,16,F"You have a bad morning, you bin it
OL,17,Fand you get on with the rest of your
OL,18,Fday, and don't let it ruin your day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
