OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"I don't know how many days I've got,
OL,7,Fhow many years I've got, you've got to
OL,8,Fenjoy it. You have to enjoy it as much
OL,9,Fas you can."
OL,11,FThe cricketing legend recently
OL,12,Fattended T20 Finals Day and it was the
OL,13,Ffirst time many fans had seen him
OL,14,Fsince his diagnosis.
OL,16,FHe admitted: "I was really scared. I
OL,17,Fwas wondering what would people think
OL,18,Fof me, being wheeled on in a chair? My
OL,19,Fson said 'pull yourself together Dad'"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
