OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"When they see me for the first time,
OL,7,Fa lot of people don't know what to
OL,8,Fsay. It's a shock for them. I want to
OL,9,Fsay 'I'm still the same old Syd
OL,10,Finside. The outside may have changed,
OL,11,Fbut I'm still the same old Syd'."
OL,13,FThe former fast bowler went on to say
OL,14,Fthat sometimes his his diagnosis would
OL,15,Fconfuse and anger him.
OL,17,F"Mentally, my brain is still the same
OL,18,F- it's not like dementia. I do
OL,19,Fsometimes think 'why me?'. My career
OL,20,Fwas cut short by injury and now this.
OL,21,FWhy me? What did I do wrong?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
