OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"But, on the other side, I was blessed
OL,7,Fto have played cricket for my county
OL,8,Fand country and I'm blessed that I was
OL,9,Fable to go on and run the local
OL,10,Fnightclub for 25 years.
OL,12,F"My life has been great and I can't
OL,13,Freally look back and be too
OL,14,Fdisappointed. The disease is cruel,
OL,15,Fbut it is what it is, get on with it
OL,16,Fwhile you're here.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
