OL,3,C'I can't win this fight': Cricketing
OL,4,Clegend David 'Syd' Lawrence on MND
OL,6,F"When I see my granddaughter I'm
OL,7,Fhappy, together with my wife and my
OL,8,Fson and his wife. I feel in a safe
OL,9,Fplace. When I'm around my friends and
OL,10,FI see what they're doing for me, I'm
OL,11,Fhappy."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
